If you read this, if your eyes are passing over this right now, even if we don't speak often, please post a comment with a memory of you and me. It can be anything you want, either good or bad.

When you're finished, post this little paragraph on your blog and be surprised (or mortified) about what people remember about you.

Hey guys! So I have not updated in a very long time....I guess you could say a lot of things have happened. Some bad, more good though. I think things might be getting back to the norm a little bit. 

Last weekend was the Halloween party filled with great friends and fun....oh yeah and we cant forget the booze, essential for every great bash. I had a really great time I met a few new people and caught up with some other people. 

This week was really cool.....Wednsday I hung out with Jasshole I missed her.....a lot...we did the norm went to G.Cizzle and had a grilled chee and talked for an hour or so. Thursday was nice too, Danielle and I worked and then hung out later in the evening.....I missed her as well. 

Last night was a crazy one at the cuzzies house, everyone was there. I polished off 8 beers in 3 hours, needless to say I was pretty friendly. Right now I am at work running on god knows how many hours of sleep and I am pretty sure Im still fractured a little bit. Thank god I dont have a hangover though...

I was thinking about school and stuff the other day and I really think I want to go into Photography. I really want to explore the world and I think Doing it with a camera in my hand would be the most awesome thing ever! I love taking pictures. I really might just do it I am sort of scared to leave and go other places besides home, but I think I might have to do it for myself.

Tonite is going to be fun, Alisha invited me on an adventure.

Post later.

<3 E

Well....Not much has happened since the last time. The past two weekends have been crazy drunken fun. two weekends ago I went to the Michigan game with my cousin and his girlfriend and her friend it was a good time we go drunk and painted our faces and had an awesomely fun time. St. Raphael's festival was after the game it was crazy there I always tend to forget the people I know when I go to gathering like that one, you just see so many people. 
   This past weekend was a blast, I stayed at Alisha's house with her for the weekend friday was a bonfire and saturday was great Danielle and Gen hung out with us and we went to the cuzzies house and got drunk and propositioned a few people. HA! Sunday was more or less of a chill day we just kicked it at Alisha's with a few people and smoked and watched "Robin Williams: live on broadway" it was fucking funny! then Alisha, Danielle, Jasshole and I went for a little driver and then we all headed home. 
   These good times never get old, keep em' rolling!
Well Im out smoke break time at school....lol peace
<3 E

P.S. Im going to be a cranky bitch thursday-saturday because of fucking garden city homecomming and I will have arthritis.

Hello all. There hasnt been much going on lately just school and work and chillin with friends you know same old shit. Danielle and I are talking again Im really glad I missed her there for a while. last night I chilled with Travis,Tommy and Melissa we went to Emily H German's house and sat there for a little bit. I had to pick up jessica from work at like 8:30ish so Tommy took me back to my car and I went to Mels to chill with Mel and Alisha. I was so tired though I went home at like 10:00. I woke up late today and I was fucking pissed....I wasnt even going to come to school but I figured I had to so I got my shit together and peaced. I think I might be getting sick I have been super tired lately I dont know whats up. Eh. Thomas and I broke up for good.....he hates me. I dont really know what to do about it but I guess I cant really care much if he doesnt. oh well. My lunch bell is about to ring I will post again soon. 
<3

So I havent posted in a loooong time lots has happened! Alisha Neil and I went to Canada for a week it was a good time I got a tattoo and Alisha got her nose pierced....twice. lol. All in all it was a great trip. 
  Last weekend was a crazy one over at my cousins house. haha. Mel+ a pint of captin mo's= best stripper on earth. lol. Alisha....hahahha...you need to come over with me again ;-) get some. I cant wait until next weekend. 
  Yesterday I started school at Cambridge. woop. not. It isnt to bad but its a new ajustment. I sdont really have any friends In my classes but thats not really what Im here for so I guess its a good thing I just want to get this year over with and graduate. I do like how I only have 4 classes. smoke breaks, and I only go to school tuesday-friday. Its not to bad. I get off campus lunch to, which pretty much consists of Emily and I going out to buy smokes and then comming back to play hacky sac and smoke squares. lol. kinda lame yes I know but I think Im doing better for my self but going here this year. I am actually going to try and get my shit done and whatnot. 
  I looked into this really rad college for photography in chicago. I think I might want to go there. I would miss everyone so much if I went there tho I dont know I dont want that to hold me back tho. I have always like photography a lot so maybe I will just do it and make lots of money. that woul dbe extra cool. maybe I could end up being a radical famous photographer for like a big mag or like some fashion line. Ahhhh....wishful thinking. Well my bell is about to ring and I dont want to waste anymore time rambling on about stuff....peace.

Hello all.
I havent posted in a long while but I've been busy with a lot of things. Quite a few things have happened since I last posted. Work is slow but its picking up a little bit So its not as monotonous as it was before, Alisha and I are becoming a lot closer and hanging out more often. She understands me a lot more than anyone else I know. Lost my best friend, It seems she doesnt care anymore, or ever for that matter. Maybe we are just growing different ways, maybe one day we will be kosher again, but that day is not today. It sucks. My boyfriend and I are good I guess, not much to say about that. Afew of us are supposed to be heading up to Canada for a vacation in like 2 weeks it will be a good time. I cant wait. Last night Alisha had a party at her house it was fun as hell. Lauren and I went to the store to buy smokes and snacks and we got pulled over it was so crazy. Jeremy came over with fucker Sparrow and I was happy I havent seen them in a long time. I was completely fractured last night, I had a lot of brew....and paid for it this morning. I ended up going to Warped with Alisha, we had an awesome time. Met a Monk. Tommorow is Danielle's party congrats to her Im not sure if Im attending yet. Well I have to get back to work there are some funeral pieces that have to  go out.
Peace nigga.

Okay so I havnt posted in a long time, heres the scoop....
Saturday night I was at my cousins like always and we were all having a great time so I decide that I have to go to the bathroom so I precede into the house and the baby gate was up so I try and get over it one leg no problem second leg big problem.....It got stuck on the gate and I when down and my leg stayed on the gate and twisted like never befor I had a Flamingo leg for 2.5. sick. Well It was dislocated. My knee cap was on the side of my leg sticking out about 2 inches.....So my cousin was like okay im gunna try and fix it well it didnt work I had to be rushed to the quacks at Garden City hospital.....They suck at life. They tried to put it back in without sadating me twice that didnt work because I screamed bloody murder so they gave me some goooooooood drugs and I went to sleep and woke up all better. Im on crutches and I have a big brace on. The past 4-5 days have been hectic with all the doctors appointments.....crazy....I think it might be a sign though for me to just chill for awhile. call me nuts but I think it is....why you ask? Well because every fucking person there that night tripped over that god damned gate and Im the only one who got hurt. Fuck. I really think its time for me to chillax for a bit. No more Pot or drinking for awhile. it will be hard but I can do it. Well Im off to get a new brace for my knee.....talk to everyone later. Pray for my leg! And thanks for all the help everyone has given me I looooove you guys! you know who you are!

Hello friends....Whats happening? Well not really anything new and exciting in my life. I have been keeping busy I guess. Friday I hung out with Alisha we went over to my cousins house and chilled for a few then we went to Princess Ninja Mel's house and hung out with BLUFF....lol. fun night after time with BLUFF we went to G.C. Cafe' and ate Danielle, Lauren , and Vince met us there. They were funny. Yesterday I went and got my hurr did and came home and took a hella long nap. When I woke up mom made me go get Mexican fiesta carry-out it was soooo good. After I ate Tom and P.T. came and got me. We chilled and drove around for awhile then we wnt to pick up this shnetler kid.....kinda weird. We walked out into the woods to this abandon houe and shit it as so fucking scary. I was wigging out. So then Tom and I dropped off schnet and P.T. and he came back to my house and chilled with me. We watched "The day after tomorrow" It was good. I <3 Jake Gyhllenhal. How cute. Im going to marry him. Tom left at like 1:00am And then I went to bed I was sleepy. Today mom and I went shopping and then out to eat at Olive garden I like that place its kinda good. I got Chicken marsala my favorite. And teramisu for dessert. Yumm. Yeah so Thursday night I came home at like 11:00 and my dad kinda got a little angry. So I cant use the truck this week. Oh well I twas worth it. Anyways... My life is kinda confusing right now. I dont know what to do about a lot of things. I still have a crush....a pointless one...Why are my crushes always pointless....I suck at the whole guy thing. Whatever I guess. Ill write again soon.
